# ==============================================================================
# Multi-Project Root .gitignore for Clover PERN Stack
# ==============================================================================
GEMINI.md

# ─── DEPENDENCY DIRECTORIES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never commit third-party packages. They are restored using 'npm install'.
node_modules/
backend/node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/

# ─── ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES & SECRETS (CRITICAL) ────────────────────────────────
# Crucial protection to keep your PostgreSQL passwords and API keys out of GitHub.
.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local
backend/.env
frontend/.env

# ─── PRODUCTION BUILDS (FRONTEND) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Exclude the compiled static production files generated by Vite.
frontend/dist/
frontend/dist-ssr/
*.cache

# ─── LOGS AND RUNTIME DIAGNOSTICS ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ignore log dumps generated during crashes or processing actions.
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ─── PRISMA SPECIFICS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Keep local SQLite binaries or testing data dumps out of the repository history.
# Note: Keep 'backend/prisma/migrations/' tracked so your database structure is saved!
*.db
*.db-journal

# ─── OPERATING SYSTEM & IDE SETTINGS ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Exclude folder configuration files specific to your computer or editor.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Code editor configurations
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.swp